dcterms:description: The Human Connectome Project (HCP) dataset provides comprehensive data on brain connectivity and function, allowing for in-depth analysis of functional MRI (fMRI) time series.
dcterms:title: Human Connectome Project (HCP) dataset

dcterms:description: The ID1000 dataset from the Amsterdam Open MRI Collection (AOMIC) consists of multimodal MRI datasets aimed at individual difference analyses, particularly during task-based fMRI scans.
dcterms:title: ID1000 dataset from Amsterdam Open MRI Collection (AOMIC)
